**Publishing:**
1. Save this draft file
2. Run `npm start` and select "Publish draft"
3. The publish script will:
   - Generate proper frontmatter (title, description, tags, featured_image)
   - Convert to MDX format
   - Move to src/content/posts/
   - Add timestamp to filename
